    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《寿司餐厅》中制作寿司，解锁新食谱，并聘请一位服务员帮忙。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作寿司，每日解锁新的食谱。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/e124e34af5ae6fc8edce74fc64cb87a7.poster.avif?t=1769100016\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/e124e34af5ae6fc8edce74fc64cb87a7.webm?t=1769100016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/e124e34af5ae6fc8edce74fc64cb87a7.mp4?t=1769100016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聘请一位服务员为你工作。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/f46ede846529c9faa7808043e795150a.poster.avif?t=1769100016\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/f46ede846529c9faa7808043e795150a.webm?t=1769100016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/f46ede846529c9faa7808043e795150a.mp4?t=1769100016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有什么东西让气氛变得一天比一天诡异。你能找出原因吗？ </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/173df535b2f6825e350e0040b7133e41.poster.avif?t=1769100016\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/173df535b2f6825e350e0040b7133e41.webm?t=1769100016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307830/extras/173df535b2f6825e350e0040b7133e41.mp4?t=1769100016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩法：制作寿司，聘请一位服务员招待顾客，解锁新的食谱。气氛变得越发诡异，你需要找出造成这一切的神秘原因。</p>",
